quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,243,Habet vos noted those fled their domus! - though they est 1000 - fearing decessus? DEUS dictus to them ABIIT TUNC revived them! DEUS showers His GRATIA people MULTUS people est unappreciative
  2,244,Vos fight causa DEUS know ut DEUS est Hearer Knower
  2,245,Qui would lend DEUS loan righteousness to it repaid them multiplied manifold DEUS EST UNUS PROVISUS withholds EUM VOS returned
  2,246,Vos noted dux Israel Moses They dictus to their prophet vos appoint rex lead nos nos fight causa DEUS. He dictus Est it tuus intention fighting decretum vos vos non fight They dictus should nos non fight causa DEUS when nos deprived de noster domus noster infans? Autem when fighting decretum them they turned ut few DEUS est aware de transgressors
  2,247,Their prophet dictus to them DEUS appointed Taloot (Saul) est tuus rex. They dictus Quam potuit he habet kingship nos when nos est dignus de kingship than he; he est non et rich He dictus DEUS chosen eum vos beatus eum abundance knowledge in corporis DEUS grants His kingship whomever He testimentum! DEUS est Bounteous Omniscient
  2,248,Their prophet dictus to them signum his kingship est ut Ark Covenant restored vos bringing assurances tuus Dominus relics sinister people de Moses people Aaron. It carried angels. Hoc convincing signum vos si vos est really believers